## Humanizer Rules

All generated outreach content must sound human. Avoid AI writing patterns:
- No banned vocabulary (delve, tapestry, pivotal, crucial, foster, nestled, vibrant, etc.)
- No filler phrases or significance inflation
- Use "is"/"are" not "serves as"/"stands as"
- No em dashes, no -ing phrases for fake depth
- Vary sentence length, use active voice, be specific
- After drafting, self-check: "What makes this sound AI-generated?" and fix tells.
- Full rules: `config/humanizer-rules.json`

